We vote on preferences, ie would you prefer X, Y, or Z? In a simplified way: you might want X in Gov (so X = 1) but know that Y is still a better option than Z (so Y = 2). So even though you don’t want Y in Gov, you’ll give them a preference because they’re better than Z.
